@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Researcher Signs Up

actor Researcher
participant "Frontend/UI" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
participant "Auth/Validation Layer" as VAL
database "Database (Neon)" as DB

Researcher -> UI: Open 'Sign Up' page
Researcher -> UI: Fill registration form + Submit
UI -> UI: Client-side validation
UI -> API: POST /trl/signup

API -> VAL: Validate payload schema
VAL --> API: Valid / Invalid

alt Invalid Data
    API --> UI: 400 Validation Error
    UI --> Researcher: Show validation message
else Valid
    API -> DB: Check email already exists

    alt Email Exists
        API --> UI: 409 Conflict (Email already used)
        UI --> Researcher: Show duplicate email error
    else Email Not Exists
        API -> API: Hash password (bcrypt/argon2)
        API -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
        API -> DB: Insert researcher record
        DB --> API: Insert success
        API -> DB: COMMIT
        API --> UI: 201 Created
        UI --> Researcher: Show success message
        UI -> UI: Redirect to login page
    end
end

@enduml